728201f-a.title: Queens: Willets Point Boulev - 38th Avenue
728201f-a.text:
Willets Point Boulevard, east side, at 38th Avenue, showing the Washington Welding Works and the J.J. Burke coal silo. In the background of view 2 is the W. and J. Sloane warehouse in Flushing.

P. L. Sperr            View 1: October 18, 1936
View 2: September 30, 1935
